parameter.name: string 1st
parameter.value: Two roads diverged in a yellow wood,

parameter.name: string 2nd
parameter.value: And sorry I could not travel both

parameter.name: string 3rd
parameter.value: And be one traveler, long I stood

parameter.name: string 4th
parameter.value: And looked down one as far as I could

parameter.name: string 5th
parameter.value: To where it bent in the undergrowth.
